                        <interp inst="t18480131-name-109" type="given" value="ROBINSON"></interp>ROBINSON WEBB</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Aug., 1847, and confined three months</hi>)—he is the man—he had had three months before that.</p>
